## Statistical Testing (15 runs across 5 seeds)
- True average: ~3.30 (NOT 8.64, variance was inflating v93 result)
- Wipeout rate: ~20-30% of runs
- Good runs (>10): ~15-20% of runs
- The game has massive internal randomness that dwarfs config differences

